  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Drug interactions between antiretroviral drugs and concomitants drugs and between
      antiretroviral need to be studied HIV-population is ageing. The referential of interactions
      is the Liverpool base.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Filters in the French social security system database, 2016 :

        -  Code of Pathology &quot;Human Immunodeficiency Virus (HIV) infection&quot; Age â‰¥ 65 years

        -  Treatment with an antiretroviral between January 1, 2016 and December 31, 2016
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
